  <section>
    <h2>Company Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Founded by <strong>Parmanand Prasad Gupta in April 1994</strong>, Bright Metal & Ferro Alloys has established itself as a trusted name in the supply of high-quality ferro alloys, metals, minerals, and industrial materials. With over three decades of experience, we cater to industries including steel manufacturing, foundries, casting units, refractory production, and chemical processing.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our commitment to quality, reliability, and customer satisfaction has made us a preferred partner across India and abroad.
    </p>
