  <section>
    <h2>Our Products</h2>
    <h3>Ferro Alloys & Metals</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Ferro Silicon</strong> – Improves strength & corrosion resistance in steel.</li>
      <li><strong>Ferro Manganese</strong> – Enhances hardness and strength in steel.</li>
      <li><strong>Silico Manganese</strong> – Deoxidizer and alloying agent for steelmaking.</li>
      <li><strong>Ferro Chrome</strong> – Essential for stainless steel; improves resistance to corrosion.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Minerals & Refractory Materials</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Bentonite Powder (Sodium Base)</strong> – Used in foundry, drilling, and iron ore pelletizing.</li>
      <li><strong>Graphite Scrap</strong> – Applied in steel refining, brake lining, and lubrication.</li>
      <li><strong>Acidic Ramming Mass</strong> – Thermal shock-resistant lining for induction furnaces.</li>
      <li><strong>Basic Ramming Mass</strong> – Ideal for lining basic induction furnaces.</li>
      <li><strong>Perlite Slag 30</strong> – Slag conditioner & insulator in steel/foundry applications.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Other Products</h3>
    <p>Carbon additives, metallurgical coke, and other mineral-based industrial inputs.</p>
  </section>

